### Edge cases
- Photo upload fails → show error toast, keep form state
- No photo AND no caption → disable Post button
- Caption only (no photo, no recipe) → postType = 'milestone'
- Photo + recipe → postType = 'photo_upload'
- Photo without recipe → postType = 'photo_upload' (recipeId omitted)
- Recipe search returns empty → show 'No recipes found'
- Large file (>5MB) → show error before upload attempt (client-side check)

