- Given auth'd user on /feed, Then FAB visible bottom-right
- Given tap FAB, Then Drawer opens with photo upload + caption + recipe picker
- Given photo selected, Then preview shows with remove option
- Given 'Link a recipe' tapped, Then search input appears with results
- Given recipe selected, Then chip appears; tap X removes it
- Given Post tapped with photo, Then photo uploads → post created → drawer closes → feed refreshes
- Given Post tapped with caption only (no photo), Then post created as milestone
